    "description": "《8号乐元》提供大量UGC的魅力元素，是一颗实现梦想和创意的星球 ٩(◦`꒳´◦)۶<br><br>没有特定的剧本，自由展开各种不同的活动、建立自己的社交圈<br><br>冒险并探索星球，建构迷人氛围的疗癒世界<br><br>在如童话般却又真实的星球裡，展开梦想新生活！<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2></strong><br><strong>潮玩风格 ★ 捏出可爱的自己</strong><br><br>高自由和细腻的角色诞生过程，撞脸机率趋近于零！<br><br>除了外貌可以选择，人种和年龄也能自己决定，搭配出隐藏版角色还有对应的特殊行为动作。<br><br>服装和饰品也可以设计与製作，加上染色剂助攻，创造出外观的无限可能。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/3103f95ae47991d95884503674d76a2d.poster.avif?t=1709285532\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/3103f95ae47991d95884503674d76a2d.webm?t=1709285532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/3103f95ae47991d95884503674d76a2d.mp4?t=1709285532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/51f4c82485f0e95a1f4da9c14dc70618.poster.avif?t=1709285532\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/51f4c82485f0e95a1f4da9c14dc70618.webm?t=1709285532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/51f4c82485f0e95a1f4da9c14dc70618.mp4?t=1709285532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>语音视讯 ★ 聊天互动主题房</strong><br><br>挑一间有兴趣的主题房加入吧！<br><br>拿起麦克风展现好声音、分享穿搭妆发、进入天黑请闭眼桌游房，还有更多的房间等你发掘。<br><br>如果不是天生的话匣子，也可以低调安静的享受这一切娱乐氛围❤<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/7a836f135e105ae4c6ef483c11fa72a5.avif?t=1709285532\" width=600 height=280 /></span><br><br><strong>创作UGC ★ 化身疯狂设计师</strong><br><br>就用 32 x 32 Pixel Art 自己动手设计吧！<br><br>探索和冒险中找到的图纸与材料，可以打造出任何东西。也能用绘图板工具自由发挥想像力完成原创作品。<br><br>如果运气好的话，製作过程中还能替道具赋加一些有趣的效果 ◍•ᴗ•◍<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/adc2666d105daa90bed9e4017b966ec3.avif?t=1709285532\" width=450 height=326 /></span><br><br><strong>宠物PIYA ★ 疗癒的贴身秘书</strong><br><br>让 PIYA 帮你蒐集各种材料和元素吧 ❤ <br><br>不仅是亲密伙伴，更是协助生产的小助手。清洁、餵食、一起冒险，增加好感度并派遣探索世界。<br><br>别忘了还能去PIYA竞技场和其他星球居民来场可爱爆表的友谊赛！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/4289cf73865b631988d979509e5995b6.poster.avif?t=1709285532\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/4289cf73865b631988d979509e5995b6.webm?t=1709285532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/4289cf73865b631988d979509e5995b6.mp4?t=1709285532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>温馨小屋 ★ 全新的梦想生活</strong><br><br>选择一块土地，成为自己的私密空间！<br><br>傢俱不只是摆设更具备实用功能，和煦的午后就在庭院来场下午茶聚会。<br><br>如果不想盖小屋，也可以开设商铺当老闆，或是建设游乐场成为娱乐霸主，打造自己的王国。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/7fafc4055865c0cfb416dca480561cdb.poster.avif?t=1709285532\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/7fafc4055865c0cfb416dca480561cdb.webm?t=1709285532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/7fafc4055865c0cfb416dca480561cdb.mp4?t=1709285532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/49fbbf839aef6e473485b1ccaea0e806.poster.avif?t=1709285532\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/49fbbf839aef6e473485b1ccaea0e806.webm?t=1709285532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/49fbbf839aef6e473485b1ccaea0e806.mp4?t=1709285532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>农牧经营 ★ 花卉农艺样样行</strong><br><br>开拓和装饰农牧场，体验四季变换的田间原野！<br><br>饲养动物生产毛绒(呢)或奶蛋製品，栽培农作物并加工成原料，记得浇水灌溉，并保持警戒以防蝗虫入侵。<br><br>或到湖边钓鱼、山林伐木、野外挖矿和採摘。完成米其林料理或隐藏烘焙菜单，会有意想不到的惊喜。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/15dba06c9f220388e9a0d72535edd6fb.poster.avif?t=1709285532\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/15dba06c9f220388e9a0d72535edd6fb.webm?t=1709285532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316300/extras/15dba06c9f220388e9a0d72535edd6fb.mp4?t=1709285532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
